#: 21337012-0-701
msgctxt "21337012-0-701"
msgid "To open the gate in our mysterious lake,"
"\n"
"\nOne must follow the book of teachings."
"\n"
"\nFor only when shapes are set and directions followed,"
"\n"
"\nWill the portal open—but try not to get swallowed."
"\n"
"\n"
"\nLet the Sun's spiky rays warm the Northern shore,"
"\n"
"\nAs Masser's Full Moon rises in the Western expanse,"
"\n"
"\nAnd Aetherius' Star sparkles above the Eastern moor,"
"\n"
"\nWhile the Crescent Moon of Secundus fills the Southern glance."
msgstr "我らの謎めいた湖の門を開けるには\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n教えの本に従わなければならない\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n形が決まり、方向が守られた時にのみ\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nポータルは開くだろう。だが呑みこまれないように\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n太陽のとげとげしい光で北の岸を温めろ\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nマッサーの満月が西の野に昇るときに\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nそしてエセリウスの星が東の湿地の上に輝き\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nセクンドゥスの三日月が、南の輝鉱を満たしている間に"

