msgid "6th Morning Star 2E 292"
"\n"
"\nArandore was right!"
"\n"
"\nManipulating the stone is a matter of casting an appropriate Conjuration spell. Construction of the city can begin in earnest."
"\n"
"\n8th Sun's Dawn"
"\n"
"\nThe wildlife in the jungle has grown nettled—perhaps understandably so, due to the work. We'll need to move faster. The sooner we complete colonization of this region, the better."
